Caused by: java.net.URISyntaxException: Illegal character in opaque part at index 7: &lt;a href=&quot;file:C:devcodekaraf-testtargetassembly/etc/f9a8234a-cebf-45b5-9316-2345d36febcd.xml&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;file:C:\dev\code\karaf-test\target\assembly/etc/f9a8234a-cebf-45b5-9316-2345d36febcd.xml&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
	at java.net.URI$Parser.fail(URI.java:2848)&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;:1.8.0_40&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
	at java.net.URI$Parser.checkChars(URI.java:3021)&lt;span class=&quot;error&quot;&gt;&amp;#91;:1.8.0_40&amp;#93;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
