                            <comment id="14616683" author="jonathan byrne" created="Tue, 7 Jul 2015 13:24:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The issue caused by Windows style paths being used in file URLs.  The fix is simply to replace the back slashes (&quot;\&quot;) with forward slashes (&quot;/&quot;) when the various path properties are set in the ConfigProperties class.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14973747" author="ffang" created="Mon, 26 Oct 2015 05:29:28 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I&apos; like to replace with toURI().toString() instead, as the toURI() can handle/escape more special chars like whitespace in windows path&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14973866" author="ffang" created="Mon, 26 Oct 2015 07:47:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;commit fix&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf/karaf/commit/536e1231&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://git-wip-us.apache.org/repos/asf/karaf/commit/536e1231&lt;/a&gt; for master&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
