&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/karaf/pull/112&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/karaf/pull/112&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Reverted changes of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-3812&quot; title=&quot;Exception caused by featuresRepositories property being set incorrectly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KARAF-3812&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KARAF-3812&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Reverted changes of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KARAF-3812&quot; title=&quot;Exception caused by featuresRepositories property being set incorrectly&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KARAF-3812&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KARAF-3812&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to let the karaf service start again if the path contains spaces under Windows.&lt;/p&gt;

